      <title>澳大利亚证券投资委员会 (ASIC) 称，不透明的澳大利亚私人市场带来巨大风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/opaque-australian-private-markets-pose-outsized-risk-asic-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚私募市场在快速扩张的同时，也给越来越多的投资者带来了巨大的潜在风险，成为该国证券监管机构的政策重点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/opaque-australian-private-markets-pose-outsized-risk-asic-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 14:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
